OL,3,CReform storm to victory in St Helens
OL,4,Cwinning majority
OL,6,FReform UK has captured the Labour
OL,7,Fstronghold of St Helens.
OL,9,FLabour had run the town since 2010 but
OL,10,Flost all but two seats.
OL,12,FReform leader Nigel Farage visiting
OL,13,Fthe town hailed his party's results.
OL,15,FHe said: "I desperately wanted to be
OL,16,Fin the Red Wall this afternoon after
OL,17,Fwhat had been a very dramatic set of
OL,18,Fresults, last night and they are still
OL,19,Fgoing on today.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
