OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778343067
OL,3,CReform storm to victory in St Helens
OL,4,Cwinning majority
OL,6,F"We have absolutely torn the most
OL,7,Fmassive historic chunk out of the
OL,8,FLabour vote in the north of England. I
OL,9,Flook at places in the North West,
OL,10,Fplaces like Tameside, and elsewhere
OL,11,Fand we are winning a remarkable number
OL,12,Fof seats."
OL,14,FReform won 34 of the 46 seats
OL,15,Favailable in the all out elections,
OL,16,Fthe Lib Dems and Independents taking
OL,17,Fthe other 10.
